  "commentary": {
    "neutral_announcer_espn": "A prolonged dink battle unfolds at the net, showcasing impressive consistency from both players. The rally emphasizes patience and control, with neither competitor willing to force an error. This is a true test of endurance and precision at the kitchen line.",
    "hype_announcer_charged": "WOAH! Look at this DINKFEST! These players are going back and forth, back and forth, at the kitchen! It's a marathon of soft hands and pure grit! Who's gonna blink first?! This is pickleball at its finest!",
    "coaching_breakdown": "Notice the controlled depth on these dinks. Both players are keeping the ball low and in the kitchen, forcing the opponent to hit up. The key here is consistency and waiting for the right opportunity to change pace or attack. We need to see more variation in pace and placement to break this down.",
