    "ron_burgundy_voice": "Well, it appears we are witnessing a rather\u2026 extended exchange of what the youngsters call 'dinks.' It's a delicate dance, much like a jazz solo, but with less saxophone and more\u2026 blue court. Truly a spectacle of controlled aggression, or perhaps, the absence thereof.",
